data.description: Sun and fun awaits in this warm and inviting and move-in ready Lake cottage nestled on 2+ private acres in Lumpkin county. Boat and fish on Lake Lanier or hang out on your single slip dock with party deck. Kayak or paddle board up the Chestatee River. Explore Dahlonega's gold country, North Georgia wine country, the north Georgia mountains or shop at the Dawsonville Outlet mall, all just minutes away.  In the evening gather around the firepit or enjoy the hot tub in your secluded back yard.    Perfect for permanent staycation home, vacation getaway 2nd home or bed & breakfast investment opportunity.    Plenty of parking with detached 2 garage and oversized steel outbuilding with room for your RV, boats and other toys.  The house features hardwood floors throughout, covered front porch, open floor plan and updated kitchen/master bath.
